##Mole Relationships in Formulas


1.  How many aluminum ions in a formula unit of aluminum selenide, [``\mathrm{Al_2Se_3}``]? [___________]{2} aluminium ions

    How many selenide ions are in a formula unit of aluminum selenide, [``\mathrm{Al_2Se_3}``]? [___________]{3} selenide ions
     
    How many moles of aluminum ions are in a mole of aluminum selenide, [``\mathrm{Al_2Se_3}``]? [___________]{2} moles aluminium ions
     
    How many moles of selenide ions are in a mole of aluminum selenide, [``\mathrm{Al_2Se_3}``]?  [___________]{3} moles selenide ions
    
    
    
2.  How many carbon atoms are in a molecule of propane, [``\mathrm{C_3H_8}``]?  [___________]{3} carbon atoms

    How many hydrogen atoms are in a molecule of propane, [``\mathrm{C_3H_8}``]?  [___________]{8} hydrogen atoms
    
    How many moles of carbon atoms are in a mole of propane, [``\mathrm{C_3H_8}``]?  [___________]{3} moles carbon atoms
    
    How many moles of hydrogen atoms are in a mole of propane, [``\mathrm{C_3H_8}``]?  [___________]{8} moles hydrogen atoms

    



END_PGML




